1166

 

Field identifier (Name):

1166 (VESSEL TYPE)

 

 

Definition:

A STANDARD DESIGNATOR USED BY NATO FORCES TO DESCRIBE SHIPS AND OTHER WATER-BORNE VESSELS FOR PLANNING AND REPORTING PURPOSES.

None

 

 

Remarks:

None
